00:32.667 --> 00:36.167
[ Voice ]
Hannah.

00:36.667 --> 00:37.507
Hannah.

00:40.200 --> 00:42.367
[ Screaming ]

00:42.367 --> 00:45.700
You know, where I come from
we usually just say hello.

00:48.300 --> 00:50.633
Danny! Look out!

00:50.633 --> 00:52.067
Ooh!

00:53.067 --> 00:55.033
[ Groaning ]

00:57.500 --> 00:59.433
[ Hannah ]
Is somebody here?

01:00.433 --> 01:01.153
Hello?

01:03.400 --> 01:04.900
I guess you're Danny's mom.

01:04.900 --> 01:06.967
I'm Hannah, your neighbor.

01:07.967 --> 01:11.467
You're not listening to me
because you're not really here.

01:11.467 --> 01:13.833
You're a ghost too.

01:13.833 --> 01:15.700
Hannah, hold on.

01:15.700 --> 01:18.800
- You said you lived at 49, right?
- Right.

01:18.800 --> 01:21.300
49 Cordina Way
burned down three years ago.

01:22.300 --> 01:23.050
No.

01:27.000 --> 01:29.700
Hannah, don't. It's not safe.

01:38.567 --> 01:41.633
You're right.
There is a ghost around here.

01:42.633 --> 01:43.713
It's you.

01:53.833 --> 01:55.800
I don't know what's going on
around here,

01:55.800 --> 01:58.300
but I know I live in that house.

02:03.200 --> 02:05.667
Danny, are you coming?

02:06.667 --> 02:09.800
Danny! Thanks.

02:09.800 --> 02:12.300
Thanks a lot.

02:22.400 --> 02:24.067
[ Sighing ]

02:38.567 --> 02:42.567
This isn't really happening.
It's not true.

02:56.067 --> 02:57.800
[ Whimpering ]

02:57.800 --> 03:00.300
[ Screaming ]

03:29.200 --> 03:30.700
It's true.

03:31.200 --> 03:33.200
I am a ghost.

03:33.700 --> 03:35.200
And I'm alone.

03:35.200 --> 03:38.700
[ Voice ] Don't be sad, Hannah,
you'll always have me.

03:39.200 --> 03:43.700
- Who are you?
- No one. A spirit.

03:43.700 --> 03:45.867
Why have you been following me?

03:45.867 --> 03:49.333
I must speak with you and
I didn't want to scare you.

03:49.333 --> 03:53.333
- What do you want?
- To help you. To teach you.

03:53.333 --> 03:55.367
To teach me what?

03:55.367 --> 04:00.233
- How to be a ghost.
- [ Thunder Clapping ]

04:00.233 --> 04:02.233
[ Wind Howling ]

04:02.733 --> 04:06.233
I don't understand.
Everything was normal.

04:06.233 --> 04:09.467
I sat right over there
and wrote a letter to Katie.

04:09.467 --> 04:12.900
So you thought.
Before you knew what you were,

04:12.900 --> 04:15.900
you kept going through the motions
of your life, day after day,

04:15.900 --> 04:18.899
unaware that the things
around you had changed.

04:19.399 --> 04:23.367
But now, no one can hear you.
No one can see you.

04:23.367 --> 04:26.467
That's not true.
Danny can see me.

04:26.467 --> 04:29.900
Stay away from him!
Danny Anderson is not your concern.

04:29.900 --> 04:33.700
- But he's my friend.
- You no longer have any friends.

04:33.700 --> 04:35.933
Without me, you have nothing.

04:37.367 --> 04:38.600
[ Knocking At Door ]

04:39.767 --> 04:42.300
- Hi.
- Go away!

04:45.800 --> 04:47.800
[ Sighing ]

04:49.533 --> 04:51.900
- Cool!
- What do you want from me?

04:51.900 --> 04:53.867
Come on, don't be so weird.

04:53.867 --> 04:57.367
- We need to talk about this.
- Get out of my house.

04:58.500 --> 05:00.200
Danny!

05:02.133 --> 05:04.533
[ Panting ]

05:05.533 --> 05:07.833
Danny, why are you acting like this?

05:07.833 --> 05:10.633
Stay back, OK?
Just stay away from us.

05:10.633 --> 05:13.333
Garlic?
What do you think I am, a vampire?

05:17.333 --> 05:19.467
Nobody, Mom.
I'm not talking to anybody.

05:19.467 --> 05:20.833
Thanks.
Thanks a lot.

05:20.833 --> 05:23.200
What do you want anyway?

05:23.633 --> 05:24.633
Ten minutes ago, we were friends,

05:24.633 --> 05:26.200
and now you're treating me
like I'm some kind of a--

05:26.700 --> 05:28.133
Ghost?

05:28.133 --> 05:30.033
OK, so I'm a ghost.

05:30.033 --> 05:31.900
Why are you the only one
who can see me?

05:31.900 --> 05:34.300
I don't know. Ghost rules?

05:34.300 --> 05:36.300
I need to find out why.

05:36.300 --> 05:37.867
Will you help me?

05:38.367 --> 05:40.500
Look, Hannah, I just don't think you
should be coming around here anymore.

05:40.933 --> 05:42.800
Are you telling me to get lost?

05:47.300 --> 05:50.000
I don't need to see a doctor,
Mom.

05:50.000 --> 05:52.000
All right, that's just great.

05:52.000 --> 05:55.033
I guess I won't be seeing you
around here after all.

05:58.533 --> 06:00.900
Nothing, Mom. Just the wind.

06:04.233 --> 06:05.733
Shadow.

06:08.233 --> 06:10.233
Where are you?

06:11.733 --> 06:13.733
Come back.

06:16.233 --> 06:18.233
I need you.

06:20.533 --> 06:23.033
[ Wind Howling ]

06:23.533 --> 06:27.833
- As I said you would.
- Don't rub it in, OK?

06:27.833 --> 06:29.633
I'm ready to learn
how to become a ghost.

06:29.633 --> 06:32.133
Good, good. Let's begin.

06:32.133 --> 06:35.000
Lesson 1: Basic haunting.

06:35.000 --> 06:37.500
First, pick your victim.

06:39.500 --> 06:41.000
Hey, there.

06:41.500 --> 06:43.567
Morning, Mrs. Smith.

06:44.467 --> 06:47.600
- Here he comes.
- [ Shadow ] So I see.

06:47.600 --> 06:49.033
[ Whistling ]

06:49.033 --> 06:50.533
Are you ready?

06:51.033 --> 06:52.533
It won't work.
He'll walk right through me.

06:52.533 --> 06:57.333
- Not if you concentrate.
- [ Whistling ]

06:59.867 --> 07:02.867
[ Groaning ]

07:02.867 --> 07:04.367
Ooh.

07:05.367 --> 07:07.867
See, I told you it wouldn't work.

07:07.867 --> 07:11.367
You're holding back.
You must concentrate harder.

07:11.367 --> 07:14.133
Use all your energy,
all your strength.

07:16.133 --> 07:17.633
[ Grunting ]

07:20.133 --> 07:21.633
[ Humming ]

07:26.600 --> 07:29.000
[ Shadow ]
You can do it. Think harder.

07:35.033 --> 07:36.033
Yes!

07:46.400 --> 07:49.567
[ Chuckling ]
Ooh. Gotta quit that coffee.

08:01.233 --> 08:03.833
[ Screaming ]

08:05.333 --> 08:06.833
[ Sighing ]

08:08.333 --> 08:12.000
- I'm so tired.
- Haunting is hard work.

08:12.733 --> 08:15.167
But you'll learn to
enjoy the afterlife.

08:15.167 --> 08:17.700
[ Bicycle Bell Ringing ]

08:21.167 --> 08:23.167
No, not like this.

08:23.167 --> 08:24.667
What is it?

08:24.667 --> 08:28.167
I didn't come back as a ghost
to pull pranks on people.

08:28.167 --> 08:30.667
There's got to be some reason.

08:30.667 --> 08:32.167
Danny's the only one
who can see me,

08:32.832 --> 08:34.767
and I want to know why.

08:34.767 --> 08:36.767
Nice meeting you.

08:36.767 --> 08:38.533
Hannah, come back here.

08:39.033 --> 08:41.533
You stay away from Danny Anderson,
do you hear?

08:41.533 --> 08:43.533
Hannah?

08:47.033 --> 08:49.367
A ghost?
[ Scoffing ] In there?

08:49.367 --> 08:51.833
I'm telling you, I saw her.

08:51.833 --> 08:55.233
I talked to her and everything
you know, I heard about her.

08:55.233 --> 08:58.233
She's got three heads
and she plays the piano.

08:58.233 --> 09:01.067
Freddie, don't be such a wuss.

09:01.067 --> 09:03.633
They just make those stories up,
you know,

09:03.633 --> 09:05.533
to keep little kids from going inside,

09:05.533 --> 09:07.900
and falling through
the floor or something.

09:07.900 --> 09:09.367
It's not just stories, it's true.

09:09.367 --> 09:11.833
Yeah? So prove it.

09:11.833 --> 09:13.700
I can't.
Nobody can see her but me.

09:14.100 --> 09:17.033
Oh, really?
How convenient.

09:17.033 --> 09:20.233
I thought you were cool.
Come on, Freddie,

09:20.233 --> 09:22.667
let's leave little
Mr. Ghost Hunter here

09:22.667 --> 09:25.367
with his imaginary girlfriend.

09:25.367 --> 09:27.367
Wait, maybe I can get her
to do something.

09:27.867 --> 09:30.367
- Like what?
- I don't know.

09:30.367 --> 09:33.233
Something ghostly.
Will you believe me then?

09:33.233 --> 09:35.033
It's a start.

09:38.033 --> 09:40.033
Hannah.

09:43.533 --> 09:46.033
Hannah, are you in here?

09:50.533 --> 09:51.253
Hello?

09:57.900 --> 09:58.740
Hannah?

10:01.900 --> 10:03.900
Hannah?

10:04.400 --> 10:09.900
Well, anyway,
I just wanted to say I'm sorry

10:09.900 --> 10:13.200
about earlier,
and getting all freaky on you.

10:13.700 --> 10:14.420
And...

10:16.200 --> 10:21.800
I kinda, you know, miss you.
And I hope you're doing OK.

10:21.800 --> 10:24.300
I was just wondering

10:24.300 --> 10:27.567
if, uh, if you don't mind,
there's these two guys outside,

10:27.567 --> 10:29.567
and they don't believe in you.

10:29.567 --> 10:31.300
So I was thinking maybe
you could do something,

10:31.733 --> 10:34.133
like haunt them or something.

10:37.067 --> 10:37.817
No!

10:39.300 --> 10:40.020
Danny!

10:43.833 --> 10:44.553
Danny!

10:55.067 --> 10:57.500
Are you all right?

10:58.567 --> 11:01.533
- Yeah, are you?
- Just a little tired.

11:01.533 --> 11:04.033
I guess this old place
is worse than it looks.

11:04.033 --> 11:07.033
I guess.
You better go.

11:07.033 --> 11:08.933
Hannah,
I wanted to ask you something.

11:08.933 --> 11:11.433
I know, you want me to do things
for your friends out there.

11:11.433 --> 11:12.933
Would you?

11:12.933 --> 11:15.000
Not right now, OK?
You gotta leave.

11:15.633 --> 11:18.067
- Well when?
- Just get out of here. Now!

11:18.067 --> 11:22.567
All right. Jeez. First you saved my life
and now you're yelling at me.

11:22.567 --> 11:24.867
I'll never figure out girls.

11:25.333 --> 11:29.533
- Why did you do that?
- Why did you interfere?

11:29.533 --> 11:32.533
- To save my friend's life?
- It's too late.

11:32.533 --> 11:34.600
What is that supposed to mean?

11:34.600 --> 11:36.833
His destiny is set.
You can not change it.

11:36.833 --> 11:38.833
Why do you wanna hurt Danny?

11:38.833 --> 11:42.000
You wanted to know
why he alone can see you.

11:42.900 --> 11:45.300
[ Danny's Voice ]
Hannah.

11:45.300 --> 11:46.700
Because by midnight tonight,

11:46.700 --> 11:49.200
he is destined to leave
the land of the living,

11:49.200 --> 11:53.267
and I will at last have a shape,
a body like you.

11:53.267 --> 11:55.267
I will become a ghost,

11:55.767 --> 11:57.867
and there's nothing
you can do to stop me.

11:57.867 --> 12:00.200
And the beam fell
and she pushed me out of the way.

12:01.700 --> 12:05.700
- What?
- You got two strikes against you, man.

12:05.700 --> 12:07.867
First, you play chicken
with the mailman

12:07.867 --> 12:10.167
and almost wind up
part of the pavement.

12:10.600 --> 12:14.600
Second, you go on a simple
ghost-finding mission,

12:14.600 --> 12:17.500
and what do you know, no ghost.

12:18.500 --> 12:21.167
We're gonna have to
have a meeting about this.

12:21.167 --> 12:23.100
Frederick.

12:24.100 --> 12:26.100
Get over here.

12:32.267 --> 12:34.200
[ Both Mumbling ]

12:34.700 --> 12:37.200
OK, we've decided to give you
one more chance

12:37.200 --> 12:39.700
to prove yourself
worthy of hanging out with us,

12:40.200 --> 12:42.600
the coolest guys in town.

12:42.600 --> 12:44.100
Are you ready?

12:44.100 --> 12:46.233
I don't know, guys,
it's getting kinda late.

12:46.733 --> 12:49.233
Hey, this is a one-time only offer.

12:50.800 --> 12:52.733
Take it or leave it.

12:54.233 --> 12:57.700
- What is it?
- Stink bomb.

12:58.200 --> 12:59.700
Guaranteed to turn
your home or office

13:00.200 --> 13:03.367
into a stinking sewer of
rotten eggs and dead fish.

13:03.367 --> 13:05.367
That's right. The smell,

13:05.867 --> 13:07.100
it never goes away.

13:07.100 --> 13:10.100
And we're going to give you
the honor of setting it off.

13:10.600 --> 13:12.000
Setting it off on who?

13:12.000 --> 13:15.600
Um, who tried to
run you over the other day?

13:16.100 --> 13:17.567
You want me to
stink bomb the mailman?

13:18.067 --> 13:20.567
No one can be an official member
of this neighborhood

13:21.067 --> 13:22.567
until they mess with Chesney.

13:22.567 --> 13:24.933
It's kind of like
the law around here.

13:26.433 --> 13:29.233
Now to make things
even easier for you,

13:29.667 --> 13:31.667
Freddie has found Chesney's address.

13:32.167 --> 13:34.167
Oh, here it is.

13:34.167 --> 13:37.067
Careful, it's got--
It's got a gummy stuck on it.

13:38.067 --> 13:42.567
So, what do you say?
Are you ready to make town history?

13:56.433 --> 13:59.333
Danny was the only one
who could hear me.

14:00.000 --> 14:03.633
Danny! Look out!

14:03.633 --> 14:05.633
[ Tires Screeching ]

14:07.133 --> 14:09.633
He was the only one
who could see me.

14:10.133 --> 14:11.633
Danny!

14:11.633 --> 14:14.367
And he's had
one too many close calls.

14:20.167 --> 14:23.033
- Where do you think you're going?
- I figured it out.

14:23.533 --> 14:24.533
I know why I came back,

14:24.533 --> 14:27.533
not to be throwing mailbags around
or scaring people,

14:27.533 --> 14:31.567
- I came back to save Danny's life.
- There's nothing you can do.

14:31.567 --> 14:35.667
Danny Anderson will be gone tonight.
And I will take his form.

14:35.667 --> 14:39.167
But if it was gonna happen anyway,
then why did you push that rafter?

14:39.167 --> 14:41.167
Don't question me, Hannah.

14:41.167 --> 14:43.667
It's because you're lying, isn't it?

14:43.667 --> 14:45.767
Danny's not supposed to
be gone tonight.

14:45.767 --> 14:47.733
Admit it,
you can't wait to become Danny.

14:47.733 --> 14:51.200
You're just trying to speed things up.
You're trying to get rid of him.

14:51.200 --> 14:54.200
That's enough!
You have much to learn, child.

14:54.700 --> 14:56.700
I don't need you to teach me
how to be a ghost.

14:57.200 --> 15:00.167
I am a ghost!
And you can't stop me.

15:02.867 --> 15:05.767
[ Shadow Screaming ]

15:09.267 --> 15:11.067
Danny, are you here?

15:12.567 --> 15:13.287
Danny?

15:14.567 --> 15:17.067
Great. Where are you?

15:18.067 --> 15:20.567
"Mr. Chesney, 148 pine street."

15:20.567 --> 15:23.567
Why is he going to Mr. Chesney's?

15:25.067 --> 15:28.067
"Take one pill every four hours."
Yeah. Sure.

15:29.500 --> 15:31.100
Yeah.

15:35.233 --> 15:39.833
OK. Now all we gotta do
is wait till he's asleep.

15:42.333 --> 15:44.833
Hey, what-- Uh...

15:54.433 --> 15:55.933
[ Crickets Chirping ]

16:07.333 --> 16:09.333
[ Striking Match ]

16:11.333 --> 16:13.500
[ Whispering ]
Come on.

16:14.000 --> 16:15.633
Come on.

16:16.133 --> 16:17.367
[ Door Opening ]

16:18.100 --> 16:19.967
[ Screaming ]

16:19.967 --> 16:22.633
[ Chesney ] Anybody--
Anybody, uh, down there?

16:22.633 --> 16:24.567
Anyone?

16:25.567 --> 16:29.600
I, uh, I should warn you,
I, uh, I study karate.

16:34.067 --> 16:37.200
- [ Meowing ]
- Beauregard.

16:37.200 --> 16:40.100
[ Chesney ]
You naughty little munchkin.

16:40.100 --> 16:42.100
You gave me quite a turn.

16:42.600 --> 16:44.600
When did you get so clumsy?

16:44.600 --> 16:46.100
[ Chuckling ]

16:46.100 --> 16:47.500
Heaven sakes.

16:47.500 --> 16:50.100
Having yourself a bit of
time tonight, were you?

16:50.100 --> 16:52.867
- [ Cat Meowing ]
- Take it easy, tabby.

16:52.867 --> 16:55.300
- [ Door Closing ]
- Oh, for heaven sakes.

16:56.300 --> 16:58.767
Well, let's get some shuteye.

17:14.933 --> 17:16.400
[ Panting ]

17:32.633 --> 17:34.433
[ Coughing ]

17:37.600 --> 17:40.200
[ Fire Alarm Ringing ]

17:42.200 --> 17:45.200
Help! Fire!

17:45.200 --> 17:47.200
[ Coughing ]

17:47.200 --> 17:50.100
Mr. Chesney, wait.
Is Danny in there?

17:50.100 --> 17:52.600
It's over, Hannah.
You can't help him now.

17:52.600 --> 17:56.900
- I win.
- No. No, you don't.

17:59.433 --> 18:01.900
Danny?
Danny, are you in here?

18:01.900 --> 18:03.633
[ Glass Shattering ]

18:07.667 --> 18:09.967
[ Danny Coughing ]

18:13.267 --> 18:15.667
No!

18:19.467 --> 18:21.900
[ Panting ]

18:27.900 --> 18:30.067
I've gotta get you out of here.

18:37.167 --> 18:40.233
It's no use. I don't have
enough strength to lift you.

18:40.233 --> 18:42.533
Danny! Danny, wake up!

18:49.500 --> 18:53.500
- [ Piano Playing ]
- Oh, my goodness! D-do you hear that?

18:53.500 --> 18:55.733
There's someone inside.

18:55.733 --> 18:58.633
Please. Thank you. Oh!

19:03.933 --> 19:08.433
[ Coughing ] Hello?
Anybody... Oh. Oh, no!

19:09.933 --> 19:12.133
Come on.

19:12.633 --> 19:14.733
[ Chesney Coughing ]

19:15.733 --> 19:17.733
[ Grunting ]

19:19.700 --> 19:22.467
[ Chesney Mumbling ]

19:25.467 --> 19:28.467
- [ Woman ] Oh, my God!
- Somebody call a doctor.

19:28.967 --> 19:30.467
[ Chesney Coughing ]

19:30.967 --> 19:34.700
- [ People Chattering ]
- [ Danny Coughing ]

19:37.067 --> 19:39.433
You're gonna be all right.

19:41.100 --> 19:45.100
- [ Coughing ]
- [ Chesney ] It's-- it's gonna be OK, son.

19:45.100 --> 19:47.100
Just take it easy, Danny.
Just try to lay still, huh?

19:47.100 --> 19:49.100
It's after midnight.

19:49.100 --> 19:51.067
Do you hear that?
It's after midnight,

19:51.067 --> 19:55.700
and he's gonna be all right.
You lose. You lose!

19:55.700 --> 19:58.900
[ Shadow Screaming ]
No!

19:59.900 --> 20:02.033
Hannah,
I can't see you anymore.

20:02.500 --> 20:04.400
[ Hannah ]
Danny, I'm right here.

20:04.400 --> 20:06.700
Hannah, Hannah, where are you?

20:06.700 --> 20:10.200
- Hannah?
- Goodbye, Danny.

20:10.200 --> 20:12.867
[ Woman ]
Hannah?

20:12.867 --> 20:15.100
Hannah.

20:16.533 --> 20:20.300
You've done a good job, honey.
It's time to come home.

20:24.733 --> 20:26.867
[ Laughing ]

20:30.467 --> 20:32.967
Yeah, I'm OK.

20:35.400 --> 20:37.200
Goodbye, Danny.

20:40.133 --> 20:43.033
Thank you, Hannah.

20:44.667 --> 20:46.100
Just a friend, Mom.

20:46.100 --> 20:48.533
I'm just talking to a friend.

